	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Nov 22nd 9:55 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I love this mace. I have toasted numerous critters now and I and my friends have spent much time basking in the light from glowing red flames :)  This weapon has seriously upped my damage potential in melee and with 128 dex I get 5-7 procs (usually for the full 110 pts) each combat.  It goes very nicely with a SSoY in the other hand that I also get a couple of procs from in the fight. I can't wait for level 44 and a werewolf illusion spell from enchanter friends ... the extra 100 dex will really fire up the proc rate.<br><br>I have also noticed skill ups for instrument skills while using this weapon but my impression is that this is coincidental and Flameweaver is not the reason.<br><br>On another note (&#9835;) whether people got this weapon for alts or not is a moot point at this stage ... I was very happy to get one for this character (my main) anyway. Enjoy!!<br>&nbsp;<br>Sereglin<br>Bard of the 40th Song<br>Jesters of Fate<br>The Rathe</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
